<br>
We've all gone thru the hardship of trying to find groups, only to be asked for ports in return.  Adapt yourself, don't limit yourself to CS find a new solo spot.  If quad kitting is not an option, then single pull.  It's not the greatest of exp, but it sure beats LFG for hours on end. <p>Bolpuhr Noghri<br>
